WEBVTT

00:02:58.576 --> 00:03:02.594
dan cari contoh ironi verbal
serta sarkasme.

00:03:02.594 --> 00:03:04.383
Semoga beruntung!

00:03:04.383 --> 00:03:06.929
Aku serius, semoga beruntung.

00:03:06.929 --> 00:03:07.969
Tidak, tidak, serius,

00:03:07.969 --> 00:03:11.129
aku benar-benar berharap
kau berhasil melakukan tugas sulit ini.

00:03:11.129 --> 00:03:13.960
Oke, semoga beruntung.

00:03:13.960 --> 00:03:14.838
Kau pasti bisa!

00:03:14.838 --> 00:03:17.057
Tidak ada ironi verbal di sini.